# Handoff

When the user says `/handoff`, "make a handoff", or "write a handoff doc", read and follow `skills/handoff/SKILL.md` in the project root to generate a structured handoff document.

Output goes to `handoff_docs/handoff_YYYY-MM-DD_[short_task_name].md`.
